thread.title_full: 3D Printing: Beyond the Hype into Space

title: 3D Printing: Beyond the Hype into Space
text:
Expand Rotite Stuart Burns, Managing Director of Rotite , has created a new and innovative product that would not have been possible if it wasn't for 3D printing. He took to the TCT Show + Personalize main stage to talk about how the tech helped develop his product and how we have now moved beyond hype.
